WEBVTT

1
00:00:01.500 --> 00:00:02.900
Do you remember Wang Ming?

2
00:00:06.966 --> 00:00:09.766
Where is our previous housekeeper now?

3
00:00:09.900 --> 00:00:12.000
Prison? How did he get in?

4
00:00:12.200 --> 00:00:13.700
What does this have to do with you?

5
00:00:13.866 --> 00:00:15.266
He's my father.

6
00:00:17.400 --> 00:00:19.100
Your father is right

7
00:00:19.866 --> 00:00:20.766
I went abroad before

8
00:00:20.766 --> 00:00:22.733
My father has been your housekeeper

9
00:00:22.733 --> 00:00:23.666
When I came back

10
00:00:23.666 --> 00:00:25.333
The only time I can see my relatives

11
00:00:25.333 --> 00:00:27.766
Tell me my father is in jail

12
00:00:27.766 --> 00:00:30.500
Your father is in prison for his own crimes

13
00:00:30.600 --> 00:00:31.733
What does it have to do with us?

14
00:00:31.733 --> 00:00:33.366
What does it have to do with you?

15
00:00:33.366 --> 00:00:35.566
My father was a man of integrity all his life

16
00:00:35.566 --> 00:00:37.366
Not even a single lie

17
00:00:37.366 --> 00:00:39.800
How could someone like him make such a mistake?

18
00:00:39.800 --> 00:00:41.900
How could you do such a serious thing?

19
00:00:41.900 --> 00:00:44.100
20 years in prison for betrayal

20
00:00:44.700 --> 00:00:46.466
You said you treated me like a brother

21
00:00:46.466 --> 00:00:49.666
Then what do you Song family treat my father as?

22
00:00:50.066 --> 00:00:51.366
Your father is a good man

23
00:00:51.366 --> 00:00:52.800
Are we the bad guys?

24
00:00:52.800 --> 00:00:54.466
No real evidence

25
00:00:54.666 --> 00:00:56.033
Don't talk nonsense.

26
00:00:56.100 --> 00:00:58.900
How have I treated you since I was a child?

